	  right: 0;
	  left: 0;
	  padding: 10px;
	  border: none;
	  top: 100%;
	  visibility: hidden;
	  transform: scale(1 , 0);
	  opacity: 0;
	  min-width: 250px;
		box-shadow: 0px 50px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
	  margin: 0;
